snippet.title: Machine Learning Street Talk
snippet.description:
Welcome! We at MLST are inspired by scientists and engineers and each week we have a hard-hitting discussion with the leading thinkers in the AI space. Street Talk is unabashedly technical and non-commercial, so you will hear no annoying pitches. Corporate- speak and MBA-waffle are banned on street talk. 

We believe strongly in diversity of thought in AI, covering all the main ideas in the field, avoiding hype where possible. 

This channel is managed by Dr. Tim Scarfe, Dr. Yannic Kilcher and Dr. Keith Duggar. We all have relevant Ph.Ds in the field, we research each show thoroughly and it's a two-way conversation with our guests. We also believe in going the extra mile on production quality. 

Pod: https://anchor.fm/machinelearningstreettalk

https://www.linkedin.com/in/ecsquizor/
https://www.linkedin.com/in/yannic-kilcher-488534136/
https://www.linkedin.com/in/dr-keith-duggar/

Join our Discord (we hang out in Yannic's one): https://discord.gg/4vNEB7t
